  "description": "Topology 2: Chua's circuit. The double-scroll attractor at chaosIndex 0.65 — deep into the chaotic regime, but leash 0.70 holds the pitch center. What emerges is the Chua breathing sound from OURO-IV: a pulsing, organic quality that belongs to neither pure noise nor pure tone, the double-scroll cycling between its two wings on a timescale audible as amplitude modulation. At the edge but stable. The membrane that has found its resting breath.",
